    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next journey with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained to ensure a smooth, reliable ride. It shows only the minor, expected signs of use for its age, making it a wonderful choice for anyone seeking a dependable and stylish companion on the road.",
